dreaming is.

00:27:09.228 --> 00:27:11.030 align:middle line:84%
It's like dancing
with the unconscious.

00:27:11.030 --> 00:27:12.498 align:middle line:84%
It's not about controlling
the dream,

00:27:12.498 --> 00:27:13.899 align:middle line:90%
