00:32:00.886 --> 00:32:03.922 align:middle line:84%
So I managed to become lucid
in the recurring nightmare.

00:32:03.922 --> 00:32:06.025 align:middle line:84%
I turned to face the
source of my fear.

00:32:06.025 --> 00:32:08.827 align:middle line:84%
It dissolved and the
nightmare went overnight.

00:32:08.827 --> 00:32:11.230 align:middle line:84%
