00:32:19.738 --> 00:32:23.909 align:middle line:84%
And yeah, that was
when I realized

00:32:23.909 --> 00:32:25.444 align:middle line:90%
that I was holding a baby.

00:32:25.444 --> 00:32:28.280 align:middle line:84%
I was holding potential and if
