00:32:28.280 --> 00:32:33.419 align:middle line:84%
grow to be this incredibly
powerful aspect of my life.

00:32:33.419 --> 00:32:36.121 align:middle line:84%
So, yeah for me, near death
experience was linked to my,

00:32:36.121 --> 00:32:39.024 align:middle line:84%
sort of the kind of
genesis of my practice.

00:32:39.024 --> 00:32:42.594 align:middle line:84%
>> Lilou: And Buddhism, since
in Buddhism the, do they believe

00:32:42.594 --> 00:32:44.830 align:middle line:90%
in reincarnation, right?

00:32:44.830 --> 00:32:48.834 align:middle line:84%
