one exactly you practice

00:35:14.513 --> 00:35:18.117 align:middle line:84%
but what's the aim of it
all, really of life even?

00:35:18.117 --> 00:35:20.285 align:middle line:84%
>> Morley: Well, I
practice Tibetan Buddhism

00:35:20.285 --> 00:35:22.721 align:middle line:84%
