00:35:41.740 --> 00:35:44.476 align:middle line:84%
So he's saying, don't do
anything that hurts yourself

00:35:44.476 --> 00:35:47.679 align:middle line:84%
or others, be kind to
people and train your mind.

00:35:47.679 --> 00:35:50.082 align:middle line:84%
And then apparently in a
kind of parable the guy said,

00:35:50.082 --> 00:35:51.850 align:middle line:90%
oh even that's too many words.

