is a projection of our mind.

00:37:25.877 --> 00:37:27.846 align:middle line:90%
It's not some external demon.

00:37:27.846 --> 00:37:30.382 align:middle line:84%
It's not somebody like, you
know, hacking your mind,

00:37:30.382 --> 00:37:31.917 align:middle line:84%
all these kind of
dualistic notions we have.

00:37:31.917 --> 00:37:34.786 align:middle line:90%
It's us, however scary it seems.

00:37:34.786 --> 00:37:36.488 align:middle line:84%
You know and we go in the
lucid dream state we're going

00:37:36.488 --> 00:37:37.689 align:middle line:90%
to see ourselves warts and all.

00:37:37.689 --> 00:37:39.691 align:middle line:84%
We're going to see all
the stuff we've repressed

00:37:39.691 --> 00:37:41.793 align:middle line:84%
in the waking state we will
see in the lucid dream.

00:37:41.793 --> 00:37:44.096 align:middle line:84%
And for some people they
can't accept that so they set

00:37:44.096 --> 00:37:46.498 align:middle line:84%
up a dualism, oh a
demon came into my dream

00:37:46.498 --> 00:37:49.368 align:middle line:84%
or aliens abducted me in my
dreams and this kind of stuff

00:37:49.368 --> 00:37:53.105 align:middle line:84%
and you think, maybe but
maybe not, so acceptance

00:37:53.105 --> 00:37:55.073 align:middle line:84%
and then friendliness,
friendliness

00:37:55.073 --> 00:37:56.408 align:middle line:90%
to everything in the dream.

00:37:56.408 --> 00:37:58.844 align:middle line:84%
To know that if everything
is me then let me be friendly

00:37:58.844 --> 00:37:59.645 align:middle line:90%
towards everything.

00:37:59.645 --> 00:38:01.346 align:middle line:90%
Let me not reject the dream.

00:38:01.346 --> 00:38:04.983 align:middle line:84%
Let me not judge the dream as I
wouldn't reject or judge myself

00:38:04.983 --> 00:38:07.386 align:middle line:84%
or want to be rejected
or judged by another.

00:38:07.386 --> 00:38:10.422 align:middle line:84%
So we enter into the dream with
friendliness and with kindness.

00:38:10.422 --> 00:38:12.357 align:middle line:84%
You know once we know that
everything in the dream is us

00:38:12.357 --> 00:38:14.226 align:middle line:84%
so in some way at
least connected

