the face, no it's you.

00:38:24.770 --> 00:38:26.505 align:middle line:84%
So be kind to everything
in the lucid dream,

00:38:26.505 --> 00:38:29.941 align:middle line:84%
be friendly to the dream and
accept that it's part of you.

00:38:29.941 --> 00:38:33.278 align:middle line:84%
