three pillars to this state.

00:38:33.278 --> 00:38:36.882 align:middle line:84%
Imagine how much easier life
would be if we could accept

00:38:36.882 --> 00:38:38.984 align:middle line:84%
that the other was
just as important as us,

00:38:38.984 --> 00:38:41.887 align:middle line:84%
that we could be kind to the
other and we could be friendly.

00:38:41.887 --> 00:38:43.755 align:middle line:84%
You know, you can get to the
point where you want to be kind

00:38:43.755 --> 00:38:45.390 align:middle line:90%
and friendly to chairs.

