other dream characters,

00:39:06.478 --> 00:39:09.081 align:middle line:84%
that that chair was
just as important as me

00:39:09.081 --> 00:39:15.120 align:middle line:84%
because it was created by that
same mind, that same genesis

00:39:15.120 --> 00:39:18.056 align:middle line:84%
that created the people in the
dream also created the chairs,

00:39:18.056 --> 00:39:20.258 align:middle line:90%
and so too in this state.

