So you've got to practise like
a rehearsal ground for reality.

00:40:06.938 --> 00:40:08.707 align:middle line:84%
Let's say you're scared
of public speaking.

00:40:08.707 --> 00:40:11.343 align:middle line:84%
With the lucid dream state you
can go into the lucid dream

00:40:11.343 --> 00:40:13.345 align:middle line:84%
and practice your
public speaking

00:40:13.345 --> 00:40:16.681 align:middle line:84%
and maybe everyone will politely
clap or maybe they'll boo

00:40:16.681 --> 00:40:18.250 align:middle line:84%
and boo you and chuck
you off the stage but

00:40:18.250 --> 00:40:21.686 align:middle line:84%
you know it's just mind, it's a
perfect place to rehearse.

00:40:21.686 --> 00:40:24.356 align:middle line:84%
So in that way again we can
manifest what we want to see

00:40:24.356 --> 00:40:26.925 align:middle line:84%
in the waking state,
confidence in public speaking,

00:40:26.925 --> 00:40:28.660 align:middle line:84%
by rehearsing in
the dream state.

00:40:28.660 --> 00:40:29.961 align:middle line:90%
But at the other end

00:40:29.961 --> 00:40:32.664 align:middle line:84%
of the spectrum it
becomes more mystical.

00:40:32.664 --> 00:40:38.069 align:middle line:84%
It seems in the lucid dream
state we can plant very strong

00:40:38.069 --> 00:40:41.907 align:middle line:84%
seeds of intention that
manifest far more powerfully

00:40:41.907 --> 00:40:43.141 align:middle line:84%
in the waking state
than if we were

00:40:43.141 --> 00:40:45.377 align:middle line:90%
to set those intentions now.

00:40:45.377 --> 00:40:47.045 align:middle line:84%
You know, right now this
is quite a gross state.

00:40:47.045 --> 00:40:48.280 align:middle line:84%
You know, this feels
pretty real.

00:40:48.280 --> 00:40:49.881 align:middle line:90%
You feel pretty separate.

00:40:49.881 --> 00:40:52.751 align:middle line:84%
You know I feel like me and
you feel like me in this state.

00:40:52.751 --> 00:40:55.687 align:middle line:84%
You do feel like me
because when I was talking

00:40:55.687 --> 00:40:56.655 align:middle line:84%
about this, do you
feel like you?

00:40:56.655 --> 00:40:58.089 align:middle line:84%
I feel like me, blah,
blah, blah.

00:40:58.089 --> 00:41:00.992 align:middle line:84%
The lucid dream state,
it's much more flowing.

00:41:00.992 --> 00:41:02.093 align:middle line:84%
You know in the lucid
dream state

00:41:02.093 --> 00:41:03.895 align:middle line:84%
at least we know it
is projection whereas

00:41:03.895 --> 00:41:06.364 align:middle line:84%
in this state we kind
of think it's all real.

00:41:06.364 --> 00:41:10.101 align:middle line:84%
So because the lucid dream state
is in many ways a state closer

00:41:10.101 --> 00:41:12.604 align:middle line:84%
to an actual experience
of reality it becomes

00:41:12.604 --> 00:41:15.040 align:middle line:84%
like an echo chamber,
like one prayer said

00:41:15.040 --> 00:41:17.209 align:middle line:84%
in the lucid dream seems
to be worth a thousand

00:41:17.209 --> 00:41:19.544 align:middle line:84%
in the waking state
because you're going kind

00:41:19.544 --> 00:41:20.779 align:middle line:90%
of direct from the source.

00:41:20.779 --> 00:41:22.881 align:middle line:84%
You're going from pure
consciousness like direct

00:41:22.881 --> 00:41:25.417 align:middle line:84%
to the kind of source
consciousness.

00:41:25.417 --> 00:41:27.519 align:middle line:84%
And in Tibetan Buddhism
it's said that one moment

00:41:27.519 --> 00:41:28.753 align:middle line:90%
of spiritual practice

00:41:28.753 --> 00:41:31.623 align:middle line:84%
in the lucid dream state
is worth a one-week retreat

00:41:31.623 --> 00:41:33.024 align:middle line:90%
in the waking state.

00:41:33.024 --> 00:41:37.329 align:middle line:84%
So if we apply those
same kinds of criteria

00:41:37.329 --> 00:41:40.098 align:middle line:84%
to manifestation we can see
just how powerful it is.

00:41:40.098 --> 00:41:41.233 align:middle line:84%
You know, if you go
into the lucid dream

00:41:41.233 --> 00:41:42.767 align:middle line:90%
and call out, I am loved.

00:41:42.767 --> 00:41:43.602 align:middle line:90%
I am lovable.

00:41:43.602 --> 00:41:45.537 align:middle line:90%
I attract love into my life.

00:41:45.537 --> 00:41:47.639 align:middle line:84%
That's not just like
me saying it now.

00:41:47.639 --> 00:41:49.908 align:middle line:90%
That's like an echo chamber.

00:41:49.908 --> 00:41:52.777 align:middle line:84%
You know, that's like saying it
a 1,000 times, once you do it in

00:41:52.777 --> 00:41:55.447 align:middle line:84%
the lucid dream state, so it's a
very, very powerful place

00:41:55.447 --> 00:41:58.283 align:middle line:90%
for amplification of intent.

00:41:58.283 --> 00:42:01.519 align:middle line:84%
>> Lilou: I had another
question regarding and zip,

00:42:01.519 --> 00:42:02.420 align:middle line:90%
it went away.

00:42:02.420 --> 00:42:03.989 align:middle line:90%
What was it?

00:42:03.989 --> 00:42:07.392 align:middle line:84%
Oh my God, I was so
excited about that question.

00:42:07.392 --> 00:42:08.760 align:middle line:90%
It just went out.

00:42:08.760 --> 00:42:11.096 align:middle line:90%
What was it?

00:42:11.096 --> 00:42:14.766 align:middle line:84%
What are some other
aspects of lucid dreaming

00:42:14.766 --> 00:42:16.167 align:middle line:84%
that we haven't talked
about yet?

00:42:16.167 --> 00:42:18.103 align:middle line:84%
And it's going to
come right back up.

00:42:18.103 --> 00:42:21.773 align:middle line:84%
>> Morley: We can talk about
the spiritual practice thing.

00:42:21.773 --> 00:42:25.277 align:middle line:84%
So, the lucid dream state is
a very powerful place to do

00:42:25.277 --> 00:42:27.379 align:middle line:90%
your spiritual practice.

00:42:27.379 --> 00:42:28.613 align:middle line:90%
Let's say I'm doing kind

00:42:28.613 --> 00:42:30.982 align:middle line:84%
of a chakra meditation right
now in the waking state.

00:42:30.982 --> 00:42:33.251 align:middle line:84%
Now although the kind of new-age
scene like to tell us, oh,

00:42:33.251 --> 00:42:36.554 align:middle line:84%
chakras are in perfect
working order it isn't quite

00:42:36.554 --> 00:42:37.956 align:middle line:90%
that simple.

00:42:37.956 --> 00:42:40.292 align:middle line:84%
Now often our chakras are often
literally spinning the wrong way

00:42:40.292 --> 00:42:41.993 align:middle line:84%
or they're kind of just
termed rusty chakras.

00:42:41.993 --> 00:42:44.496 align:middle line:84%
You know, our energy systems are
quite dis-aligned unless we're

00:42:44.496 --> 00:42:47.299 align:middle line:84%
doing a lot of spiritual
practice so let's say I was

00:42:47.299 --> 00:42:50.735 align:middle line:84%
in a chakra practice in
this state things may not be

00:42:50.735 --> 00:42:52.170 align:middle line:90%
in perfect alignment.

00:42:52.170 --> 00:42:53.538 align:middle line:90%
If I do a chakra meditation

00:42:53.538 --> 00:42:57.142 align:middle line:84%
in the lucid dream state, the
chakras are in perfect alignment

00:42:57.142 --> 00:42:59.144 align:middle line:90%
because I have no physical form.

00:42:59.144 --> 00:43:01.279 align:middle line:84%
In the dream state
I'm in my dream body.

00:43:01.279 --> 00:43:05.617 align:middle line:84%
I'm in my subtle energetic form
so we reach our full potential.

00:43:05.617 --> 00:43:08.653 align:middle line:84%
You know in the lucid dream
state your chakras are perfect

00:43:08.653 --> 00:43:10.021 align:middle line:90%
so if you do chakra meditation

00:43:10.021 --> 00:43:13.458 align:middle line:84%
in the lucid dream you can
reach far greater levels

00:43:13.458 --> 00:43:15.627 align:middle line:84%
of realization and
attainment than you could

00:43:15.627 --> 00:43:19.097 align:middle line:84%
in the waking state because this
gross corporeal body stops us

00:43:19.097 --> 00:43:20.699 align:middle line:90%
doing stuff, like for one,

00:43:20.699 --> 00:43:22.334 align:middle line:84%
like you're trying
to sit in full lotus.

00:43:22.334 --> 00:43:24.102 align:middle line:84%
A lot of people unless
they're trained in yoga,

00:43:24.102 --> 00:43:25.637 align:middle line:84%
their knees will
start to hurt, right?

00:43:25.637 --> 00:43:28.573 align:middle line:84%
Lucid dream state there are no
knees so your knees won't hurt

00:43:28.573 --> 00:43:30.642 align:middle line:84%
so you can sit in
perfect posture for one,

00:43:30.642 --> 00:43:33.578 align:middle line:84%
your chakras aligned, your
energy systems are balanced

00:43:33.578 --> 00:43:35.747 align:middle line:84%
and for some people they
find, you know,

00:43:35.747 --> 00:43:37.615 align:middle line:84%
meditation in the lucid
dream state is one

00:43:37.615 --> 00:43:39.951 align:middle line:84%
of the most mind blowing
experiences they can have.

00:43:39.951 --> 00:43:41.353 align:middle line:84%
You know, in the book
I talk about this.

00:43:41.353 --> 00:43:44.255 align:middle line:84%
When I first started I could
barely sustain meditation

00:43:44.255 --> 00:43:46.424 align:middle line:84%
in the lucid dream for more
than a few seconds and I felt

00:43:46.424 --> 00:43:50.562 align:middle line:84%
like my head had been put in
a microwave, and you just woke

00:43:50.562 --> 00:43:54.966 align:middle line:84%
up with just this huge shot
of absolute bliss that led you

00:43:54.966 --> 00:43:56.935 align:middle line:90%
to wake up, so meditation

00:43:56.935 --> 00:44:00.038 align:middle line:84%
in the lucid dream state is
very, very powerful.

00:44:00.038 --> 00:44:02.374 align:middle line:84%
In fact one of the Buddhist
scholars, B. Alan Wallace used

00:44:02.374 --> 00:44:04.743 align:middle line:84%
to translate for the
Dalai Lama has said

00:44:04.743 --> 00:44:07.379 align:middle line:84%
that of the three main
states of awareness or states

00:44:07.379 --> 00:44:10.348 align:middle line:84%
of experience, sleep,
dream and waking,

00:44:10.348 --> 00:44:13.985 align:middle line:84%
the one with the least potential
for spiritual realization is

00:44:13.985 --> 00:44:15.887 align:middle line:90%
in fact the waking state.

00:44:15.887 --> 00:44:18.957 align:middle line:84%
It is easier to reach your full
potential in the sleep and dream

00:44:18.957 --> 00:44:21.326 align:middle line:84%
than the waking state
because you're closer

00:44:21.326 --> 00:44:23.828 align:middle line:84%
to enlightened nature
in the lucid dream

00:44:23.828 --> 00:44:25.330 align:middle line:84%
than you are in this
waking state.

00:44:25.330 --> 00:44:27.432 align:middle line:84%
>> Lilou: And then you
can chat with Buddha?

00:44:27.432 --> 00:44:28.633 align:middle line:90%
>> Morley: Yeah, exactly.

00:44:28.633 --> 00:44:31.436 align:middle line:84%
>> Lilou: Are you, do you
do those conversations?

00:44:31.436 --> 00:44:32.904 align:middle line:84%
>> Morley: Well, let's
say I'm in a lucid dream

00:44:32.904 --> 00:44:33.872 align:middle line:90%
and I meet Buddha right?

00:44:33.872 --> 00:44:35.573 align:middle line:84%
I've got two options
working here.

00:44:35.573 --> 00:44:38.076 align:middle line:84%
One is you're meeting
a representation

00:44:38.076 --> 00:44:39.411 align:middle line:90%
of your own higher self.

00:44:39.411 --> 00:44:41.946 align:middle line:84%
So for me, my kind of inner
archetype of higher self,

00:44:41.946 --> 00:44:44.716 align:middle line:84%
the wise man for me, would
probably look like my guru,

00:44:44.716 --> 00:44:47.485 align:middle line:84%
Lama Yeshe Rinpoche because
he's my guru archetype.

00:44:47.485 --> 00:44:48.887 align:middle line:90%
If you were really

00:44:48.887 --> 00:44:50.989 align:middle line:84%
into Christianity let's say it
might look like the Virgin Mary

00:44:50.989 --> 00:44:52.991 align:middle line:90%
for you or Jesus Christ himself.

00:44:52.991 --> 00:44:55.627 align:middle line:84%
So we could be working just
with internal archetypes.

00:44:55.627 --> 00:44:58.296 align:middle line:84%
That's still a big deal, you
know, to meet your higher self.

00:44:58.296 --> 00:45:01.533 align:middle line:84%
In whatever form, it's still a
very, very powerful experience.

00:45:01.533 --> 00:45:03.468 align:middle line:84%
And then there's the
other option which is

00:45:03.468 --> 00:45:06.604 align:middle line:84%
that the lucid dream state
is partially permeable,

00:45:06.604 --> 00:45:09.274 align:middle line:84%
very difficult for anything to
get in without you letting it

00:45:09.274 --> 00:45:10.742 align:middle line:84%
but it is possible
for your consciousness

00:45:10.742 --> 00:45:13.978 align:middle line:84%
to expand beyond the boundaries
of the lucid dream state

00:45:13.978 --> 00:45:16.481 align:middle line:84%
and enterwhat we might call
the collective unconscious,

00:45:16.481 --> 00:45:17.849 align:middle line:90%
the universal mind-steam.

00:45:17.849 --> 00:45:21.219 align:middle line:84%
It could even be about kind
of astral plains and that sort

00:45:21.219 --> 00:45:23.721 align:middle line:84%
of stuff although I don't
usually use that terminology.

00:45:23.721 --> 00:45:25.990 align:middle line:84%
So it could be in
the lucid dream.

00:45:25.990 --> 00:45:29.894 align:middle line:84%
There is the option to
engage aspects outside of you

00:45:29.894 --> 00:45:32.397 align:middle line:84%
and then you could be
looking at very powerful,

00:45:32.397 --> 00:45:35.867 align:middle line:84%
universal archetypes of
compassion such as Buddha mind.

00:45:35.867 --> 00:45:39.404 align:middle line:84%
Who's to tell the
difference, only the dreamer?

00:45:39.404 --> 00:45:41.272 align:middle line:84%
You know, you're the only one
in there, hello and people ask,

00:45:41.272 --> 00:45:43.441 align:middle line:84%
what do you think this
was in a lucid dream?

00:45:43.441 --> 00:45:45.643 align:middle line:84%
And I say, well I wasn't
there so I don't know

00:45:45.643 --> 00:45:48.580 align:middle line:84%
but I can give you hints on
what it might be but it's

00:45:48.580 --> 00:45:49.981 align:middle line:90%
for the dreamer to decide.

00:45:49.981 --> 00:45:50.815 align:middle line:90%
You know, we.

00:45:50.815 --> 00:45:51.816 align:middle line:90%
>> Lilou: How did it felt too?

00:45:51.816 --> 00:45:53.184 align:middle line:84%
I guess it's an important
question.

00:45:53.184 --> 00:45:56.988 align:middle line:84%
>> Morley: Yeah, like I've had
enough dreams of my teacher

00:45:56.988 --> 00:45:59.023 align:middle line:84%
to know when it's just
a projection of him

00:45:59.023 --> 00:46:05.063 align:middle line:84%
and when it might actually be a
connection with him, you know,

00:46:05.063 --> 00:46:07.298 align:middle line:90%
as an actual energetic being.

00:46:07.298 --> 00:46:08.967 align:middle line:84%
>> Lilou: Yeha, because often
we hear some teacher,

00:46:08.967 --> 00:46:11.102 align:middle line:84%
some spiritual teachers
here that say, oh, I'll come

00:46:11.102 --> 00:46:12.770 align:middle line:90%
and visit you during the sleep

00:46:12.770 --> 00:46:15.373 align:middle line:84%
or you'll receive
emails, you know.

00:46:15.373 --> 00:46:17.108 align:middle line:84%
I receive sometimes
emails of people saying,

00:46:17.108 --> 00:46:18.510 align:middle line:90%
you were in my dream last night.

00:46:18.510 --> 00:46:19.878 align:middle line:90%
How does that work?

00:46:19.878 --> 00:46:21.679 align:middle line:84%
>> Morley: Yes, I mean let's
say I have a lucid dream tonight

00:46:21.679 --> 00:46:22.881 align:middle line:84%
