>> Lilou: My God, come on!

00:46:25.917 --> 00:46:27.519 align:middle line:84%
>> Morley: You know,
but what does it mean?

00:46:27.519 --> 00:46:29.988 align:middle line:84%
It just means you had a lucid
dream and I had a lucid dream.

00:46:29.988 --> 00:46:30.922 align:middle line:90%
It doesn't mean anything.

00:46:30.922 --> 00:46:32.390 align:middle line:90%
It just means the projection.

00:46:32.390 --> 00:46:35.126 align:middle line:84%
However, if we were to do
that intentionally and I was

00:46:35.126 --> 00:46:37.662 align:middle line:84%
to give you a password and you
could prove that password to me

00:46:37.662 --> 00:46:39.164 align:middle line:84%
in the waking state
then we could know

00:46:39.164 --> 00:46:40.365 align:middle line:90%
that there was a connection.

00:46:40.365 --> 00:46:42.100 align:middle line:84%
So there are a lot of
password experiments going

00:46:42.100 --> 00:46:43.434 align:middle line:90%
on at the moment actually

00:46:43.434 --> 00:46:46.204 align:middle line:84%
on wakeupinyourdreams.com, a
website run by a friend of mine.

00:46:46.204 --> 00:46:48.306 align:middle line:84%
He's just started a
password experiment.

00:46:48.306 --> 00:46:50.842 align:middle line:84%
But it seems like
it is possible.

00:46:50.842 --> 00:46:52.277 align:middle line:84%
You know, the people
who seem to be able

00:46:52.277 --> 00:46:55.046 align:middle line:84%
to enter your lucid dream
if you have the intention

00:46:55.046 --> 00:46:57.649 align:middle line:84%
to let them are kind
of dead relatives.

00:46:57.649 --> 00:46:59.250 align:middle line:84%
This one seems to come
up again and again.

00:46:59.250 --> 00:47:02.020 align:middle line:84%
It's strange because I don't
have any science for this.

00:47:02.020 --> 00:47:03.655 align:middle line:84%
Usually I try and make
sure everything is backed

00:47:03.655 --> 00:47:05.456 align:middle line:84%
up by science, no
science for this.

00:47:05.456 --> 00:47:06.691 align:middle line:90%
It would be only anecdote.

00:47:06.691 --> 00:47:08.860 align:middle line:84%
It seems if you have a very
strong heart connection

00:47:08.860 --> 00:47:11.963 align:middle line:84%
or blood connection to somebody,
then when they're dead it seems

00:47:11.963 --> 00:47:14.465 align:middle line:84%
like the lucid dream state
can be a kind of a portal

00:47:14.465 --> 00:47:16.301 align:middle line:90%
for communication with them.

00:47:16.301 --> 00:47:17.702 align:middle line:84%
And the other people
who seem to be able

00:47:17.702 --> 00:47:19.070 align:middle line:84%
to enter the lucid
dream state are those

00:47:19.070 --> 00:47:20.872 align:middle line:90%
who have woken up in this state.

00:47:20.872 --> 00:47:23.775 align:middle line:84%
You know if you've reached full
lucidity in this state it seems

00:47:23.775 --> 00:47:26.144 align:middle line:84%
to give you the ability to
enter other people's dreams,

00:47:26.144 --> 00:47:28.246 align:middle line:84%
so fully awakened
masters seem to be able

00:47:28.246 --> 00:47:29.814 align:middle line:90%
to enter their students' dreams.

00:47:29.814 --> 00:47:31.983 align:middle line:84%
>> Lilou: Yeah, I'm wondering
if after a certain time

00:47:31.983 --> 00:47:36.554 align:middle line:84%
and that was my question earlier
that I forgot but how does it?

00:47:36.554 --> 00:47:38.289 align:middle line:84%
I guess it's a better
moment to ask it now

