you're doing it

00:47:53.304 --> 00:47:56.407 align:middle line:84%
so I'm not saying lucid dreaming
while you're actually talking

00:47:56.407 --> 00:47:58.943 align:middle line:84%
to me right now but you
could kind of thing,

00:47:58.943 --> 00:48:01.412 align:middle line:90%
to improve the experience?

00:48:01.412 --> 00:48:04.115 align:middle line:84%
>> Morley: Yeah, lucid dreaming
