00:48:16.628 --> 00:48:19.130 align:middle line:84%
Where's the dream, you
know, the opposite,

00:48:19.130 --> 00:48:21.132 align:middle line:84%
every time you have a lucid
dream you're training yourself

00:48:21.132 --> 00:48:23.067 align:middle line:84%
to tell the difference,
to know the difference

00:48:23.067 --> 00:48:26.804 align:middle line:84%
between waking reality,
dream reality, illusion

00:48:26.804 --> 00:48:28.506 align:middle line:84%
and the other aspect
of illusion.

00:48:28.506 --> 00:48:30.541 align:middle line:84%
So actually lucid dreamers
are often very grounded

00:48:30.541 --> 00:48:31.909 align:middle line:84%
and they're often
very pro-active.

00:48:31.909 --> 00:48:35.613 align:middle line:84%
Like if you spent your
nighttime hugging your demons,

00:48:35.613 --> 00:48:38.449 align:middle line:84%
walking through walls, flying
through the sky, the next day

00:48:38.449 --> 00:48:40.151 align:middle line:84%
at work when your boss
is giving you hell,

00:48:40.151 --> 00:48:42.153 align:middle line:84%
it's like water off a
duck's back, you know.

00:48:42.153 --> 00:48:43.688 align:middle line:84%
It's much easier to
work through this

00:48:43.688 --> 00:48:45.556 align:middle line:90%
because you feel so empowered.

00:48:45.556 --> 00:48:48.726 align:middle line:84%
You feel so limitless in the
lucid dream and you can't forget

00:48:48.726 --> 00:48:52.530 align:middle line:84%
that so you bring that sense of
limitlessness into this state

00:48:52.530 --> 00:48:55.533 align:middle line:84%
and realize that, yeah, although
I can't walk through that wall

00:48:55.533 --> 00:48:58.069 align:middle line:84%
in this state maybe I can
walk through the brick wall

00:48:58.069 --> 00:49:01.172 align:middle line:84%
of somebody's projections, or
even more importantly the brick

00:49:01.172 --> 00:49:03.308 align:middle line:84%
wall of my own projections
of my own baggage.

00:49:03.308 --> 00:49:06.377 align:middle line:84%
That it's not so solid that I
can pass through it and that

00:49:06.377 --> 00:49:08.746 align:middle line:84%
when I'm confronted by the
demons of my own arrogance

00:49:08.746 --> 00:49:11.382 align:middle line:84%
or my own fear so too
can I hug them just

00:49:11.382 --> 00:49:13.685 align:middle line:90%
like I did in the lucid dream.

