which is the Toltec symbol

00:50:07.672 --> 00:50:09.440 align:middle line:84%
of the gateway keeper
to the dream.

00:50:09.440 --> 00:50:10.508 align:middle line:90%
You've got the butterfly,

00:50:10.508 --> 00:50:11.976 align:middle line:84%
