Taoist parable,

00:50:11.976 --> 00:50:13.311 align:middle line:84%
am I the man dreaming
a butterfly,

00:50:13.311 --> 00:50:14.812 align:middle line:90%
a butterfly dreaming a man.

00:50:14.812 --> 00:50:18.449 align:middle line:84%
